= Richard, Yan-Chak Li

== Biography
*Richard Li* received Dean of Engineering Scholarship, when he was admitted into [https://www.ust.hk/ The Hong Kong University of Science and Technology (HKUST)] in 2013. He received his Bachelor degree in [http://cpeg.ust.hk/cgi-bin/eng/index.php Computer Engineering] in 2017 from [https://www.ust.hk/ HKUST]. His undergraduate study is combined with Applied Mathematics, Computer Science and Electronic Engineering. He joined [https://urop.ust.hk/ Undergraduate Research Opportunities Program (UROP)] under supervision of Prof. [http://kehlam.people.ust.hk/index.html Henry H. N. Lam] in 2017 Summer. The work was presented in Asia-Oceania Mass Spectrometry Conference 2017 with Young Scientist Travel Award.
\n
\n Currently, he is a M.Phil. student major in [https://bien.ust.hk/ Bioengineering] in [https://www.ust.hk/ HKUST].
His thesis project is building an automatic vertebral edge detection tool via Deep Learning under supervision of [https://www.ielm.ust.hk/dfaculty/so/ Prof. Richard H.Y. So].

